nodes.text: Alliance Intelligence Report: TIE Fighters is an article appearing in the May 1996 Star Wars Adventure Journal 10, written by Timothy S. O'Brien as a supplement for the West End Games Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game. Diagram illustrations were provided by Stephen Crane.
The article is written from an in-universe perspective by Rebel Alliance Lieutenant Commander Bakki Sourthol, serving as a tie-in to the West End Games sourcebook Alliance Intelligence Reports.
